data.title: Application For New Dealer License
data.text:
We have saved your application and now need to process payment. We will be redirecting you to our payment vendor to collect payment in regards to your business license application. Do not refresh or navigate away.

While at our vendors site do not close your browser, navigate away, or click your back button. Doing so will result in the voiding of your application. Once payment has been collected at our vendor's site you will be redirected back to MyDMV to complete your application.
